snippet.title: Go UrbanTerror!
snippet.description:
Fast and action packed OG Quake III style first-person shooter game with UrbanTerror. Where fun goes above realism.
Real free to play and cross-platform (Windows, Linux, MacOSX) with online and LAN multiplayer. 

Go to https://www.urbanterror.info/ now to learn more!
For competitive online play visit http://urban-zone.org/

:: music by GFYrapcore: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVLEaGnjqbZeA_dkxmLShhQ
